description:
DUTIES:
•develops and implements media and communications strategy for the Member;
•tracks current legislative and non-legislative issues about which the Member
may be questioned;
•evaluates current events and media reports in the district and the nation for their
impact on the Member;
•provides ideas and advice on the effect in the media of the Member's actions and
legislative activities;
•writes remarks for the Member; and
•performs other duties as assigned.
